Currently venv directory:
python-pip
python-virtualenv

python-pip:
1. Create a python virtual enviorment 
  python3 -m venv ~/venv/
2. Activate python virtual enviorment
  source ~/venv/bin/activate
3. To deactivate 
  deactivate
4. set in variable in bash_profile
VIRTUAL_ENV variable can be set 
5.test with...
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
